Class HttpPrincipal

java.lang.Object
com.sun.net.httpserver.HttpPrincipal
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class HttpPrincipal
extends Object
implements Principal
Represents a user authenticated by HTTP Basic or Digest authentication.
